responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "B08BA3EE465525E55291CBBF72680B0F", "Deliah the Priestess of Carnage entered the central keep where she found our finest whose orders were their last and a gift to us all. There they held her in a final stand just long enough to set our trap that would imprison the demoness in an arcane prison bound by the Seals of Sephillion. ")
